Cheshire: Now I shall have somebody to talk to!
Cheshire: How are you getting on?
Alice: I would like to know which way I ought to go.
Cheshire: Well, that depends... Where you’d like to get to?
Alice: Well, that really doesn’t matter, as long as I-
Cheshire: Well, then it really doesn’t matter which way you go.
Cheshire laughs and leaves.
Cheshire: The white rabbit went that way, if you’re unsure ask the mad hatter.
=> END